Saving Private Ryan;;95;;93;;R;;Captain John Miller (Tom Hanks) takes his men behind enemy lines to find Private James Ryan, whose three brothers have been killed in combat. Surrounded by the brutal realties of war, while searching for Ryan, each man embarks upon a personal journey and discovers their own strength to triumph over an uncertain future with honor, decency and courage.;;History,War,Drama;;Steven Spielberg;;1998;;Tom Hanks,Edward Burns,Tom Sizemore,Jeremy Davies,Vin Diesel,Adam Goldberg,Barry Pepper,Giovanni Ribisi,Matt Damon,Dennis Farina,Ted Danson,Harve Presnell,Dale Dye,Bryan Cranston,David Wohl,Paul Giamatti,Ryan Hurst,Harrison Young;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saving_private_ryan